@Beth in Greenbelt

“Not sure I even remember any other names from Roots.”

Your thinking mirrors the way constructors and editors think when they create the puzzles. Sure, there are other surnames in Roots, but only one is likely to be the answer, because there’s only one name that is significant enough to the story that people remember it fifty years after the miniseries was on TV.

